  <brief_title>Use of Fish Skin Extracellular Matrix (ECM) to Facilitate Chronic Wound Healing</brief_title>
  <official_title>Chronic Wound Treatment With Extracellular Matrix (ECM) Scaffold Made From Fish Proteins</official_title>
